Invocation Name: ok boomer
des:
Ask Alexa for boomerisms!

Ok Boomer provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you wiser and more equipped to deal with the 'real world'.

To start, just say "Alexa, ok boomer" or "Alexa, open ok boomer" to get a boomerism".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop", unlike when talking to your favorite boomer relative...
